<hr data-start="926" data-end="929">
<h2 data-section-id="jo4ivl" data-start="931" data-end="979">🥗 4. Bowl healthy (poke bowl ou buddha bowl)</h2>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour Poke bowl mangue-avocat"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://www.lesfruitsetlegumesfrais.com/app/uploads/2025/01/m1989-hd-poke-bowl-avocat-mangue.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/m1989-hd-poke-bowl-avocat-mangue.jpg" style="object-position: 50% 0%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour Buddha bowl aux légumes rôtis"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://aicdn.speedsize.com/54b53e1d-47a6-4f42-8122-1c85f7171092/https%3A//www.kazidomi.com/content/Posts_carres_MARSAVRIL_2_02fd264bf8.jpg?speedsize=mxw_1024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/lXE5MeTVyP4wG_cZWphh2wB7D3Ow5mvEa5g08YgYuOB7yrnSdylFxSLfsVCXclAwIWm8tyPpkBSJhF41f0mVWUbmdubJPuYs1Nsp0aeQg38KeaKTg44IjN1gawC6TEKDZxmxTSovHL