<p data-start="1021" data-end="1054">Très tendance et super équilibré.</p>
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1066"><strong data-start="1056" data-end="1066">Base :</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1067" data-end="1094">
<li data-section-id="1l46maa" data-start="1067" data-end="1094">
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1094">Riz, quinoa ou couscous</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1096" data-end="1108"><strong data-start="1096" data-end="1108">Ajouts :</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1109" data-end="1204">
<li data-section-id="1i327xg" data-start="1109" data-end="1131">
<p data-start="1111" data-end="1131">Légumes crus/cuits</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wk3nu" data-start="1132" data-end="1166">
<p data-start="1134" data-end="1166">Protéines (thon, poulet, tofu)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fcd01j" data-start="1167" data-end="1204">
<p data-start="1169" data-end="1204">Sauce soja, tahini ou vinaigrette</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1206" data-end="1218">⏱️ 15–25 min</p>
<hr data-start="1220" data-end="1223">
<h2 data-section-id="1c1re74" data-start="1225" data-end="1251">🍳 5. Shakshouka rapide</h2>
