ka-nos-recettes-tendances-et-express-de-ce-diner-a-la-poele.jpg" style="object-position: 54.4% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour Oeufs pochés au fromage dans une sauce tomate épicée"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://producteurslaitiersducanada.ca/sites/default/files/styles/recipe_image/public/image_file_browser/conso_recipe/2021/CHEESY%20EGGS%20POACHED%20IN%20SPICED%20TOMATO%20SAUCE.jpg.jpeg?itok=x2herKnY" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/CHEESY EGGS POACHED IN SPICED TOMATO SAUCE.jpg.jpeg" style="object-position: 27.3% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-2 bottom-2 z-0 flex max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)] flex-wrap items-end justify-end gap-1.5"><div class="shrink-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 text-white backdrop-blur-md backdrop-brightness-75"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#266724" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><span class="text-xs font-semibold">4</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="1293" data-end="1327">Un plat savoureux et réconfortant.</p>
<p data-start="1329" data-end="1348"><strong data-start="1329" data-end="1348">Astuce rapide :</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1349" data-end="1438">
<li data-section-id="1kzsuho" data-start="1349" data-end="1394">
<p data-start="1351" data-end="1394">Utilise une bonne sauce tomate déjà prête</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bj9ava" data-start="1395" data-end="1438">
<p data-start="1397" data-end="1438">Ajoute des œufs + épices (cumin, paprika)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1440" data-end="1452">⏱️ 15–20 min</p>
<hr data-start="1454" data-end="1457">
<h2 data-section-id="wng5e4" data-start="1459" data-end="1500">🫓 6. Wraps ou sandwichs chauds maison</h2>
