خليني أوضح لك الفكرة ببساطة:</p>
<hr data-start="99" data-end="102">
<h2 data-section-id="1t3ka1i" data-start="104" data-end="149">💻 1. تشغيل الموقع على جهازك (بدون إنترنت)</h2>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour HTML Tag Plugin for Notepad++: Find and Highlight Tags Easily"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://www.addictivetips.com/app/uploads/2011/08/find-matching-tags.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/find-matching-tags.jpg" style="object-position: 62.2% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour How to Open an HTML File in Google Chrome"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://images.surferseo.art/52922849-ab19-4d2c-b8bc-d60fd19a6bb5.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/52922849-ab19-4d2c-b8bc-d60fd19a6bb5.png" style="object-position: 100% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour Nostos Marketing SL (Salamanca): Info, Rankings &amp; Votes | Billionhands"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://qdengdctvmermamwtfhk.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/place-images-1/ChIJFyBc8G6XmUcRTyzzuVfD96o/photo_2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/photo_2.jpg" style="object-position: 37.8% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-2 bottom-2 z-0 flex max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)] flex-wrap items-end justify-end gap-1.5"><div class="shrink-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 text-white backdrop-blur-md backdrop-brightness-75"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#266724" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><span class="text-xs font-semibold">4</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="191" data-end="226">إذا كتبت كود HTML في <strong data-start="212" data-end="225">Notepad++</strong>:</p>
<ol data-start="228" data-end="329">
<li data-section-id="13z0snn" data-start="228" data-end="266">
<p data-start="231" data-end="266">احفظ الملف بصيغة:<br data-start="248" data-end="251">
<code data-start="254" data-end="266">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j613af" data-start="267" data-end="287">
<p data-start="270" data-end="287">اضغط عليه مرتين</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1flo2sf" data-start="288" data-end="329">
<p data-start="291" data-end="329">يفتح مباشرة في المتصفح (Chrome / Edge)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="331" data-end="392">👉 هذا <strong data-start="338" data-end="352">مجاني 100%</strong><br data-start="352" data-end="355">
لكن الموقع يظهر <strong data-start="371" data-end="391">فقط لك على جهازك</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="394" data-end="397">
<h2 data-section-id="xfswww" data-start="399" data-end="439">🌐 2. نشر الموقع للناس (مجاني أيضًا!)</h2>
<div class="no-scrollbar flex min-h-36 flex-nowrap gap-0.5 overflow-auto sm:gap-1 sm:overflow-hidden xl:min-h-44 mt-1 mb-5 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-4"><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-s-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour How to Make a Website with Github Pages | Chicago Public Library Maker Lab"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://cplmakerlab.github.io/uploads/how-to-make-a-website-with-github-pages/website-example.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/website-example.png" style="object-position: 0% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)]" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour Text Platform | Host Your Widget in 2 Minutes with Netlify Drop"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://platform.text.com/resource-center/netlify_drag_drop.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/netlify_drag_drop.png" style="object-position: 100% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative w-32 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-64 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/3)] rounded-e-xl" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 5 / 4;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Ouvrir les détails de l&#39;image pour How to Host a Web Page for Free | HTML Hosting Tips"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://unicorn-images.b-cdn.net/90d85b8c-d5d7-4f71-83fb-c7f4906424bd?optimizer=gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./sound_files/90d85b8c-d5d7-4f71-83fb-c7f4906424bd" style="object-position: 0% 50%; opacity: 1;"></div></button><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-2 bottom-2 z-0 flex max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)] flex-wrap items-end justify-end gap-1.5"><div class="shrink-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 text-white backdrop-blur-md backdrop-brightness-75"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#266724" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><span class="text-xs font-semibold">4</span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="481" data-end="558">إذا تريد الناس يشوفوا موقعك، تحتاج “استضافة” (Hosting)، لكن في خيارات مجانية:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1irk33b" data-start="560" data-end="587">🔹 أفضل الطرق المجانية:</h3>
<ul data-start="588" data-end="722">
<li data-section-id="1maqro1" data-start="588" data-end="642">
<p data-start="590" data-end="642"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span> (GitHub Pages)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1etlrsl" data-start="643" data-end="682">
<p data-start="645" data-end="682"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fetjdh" data-start="683" data-end="722">
<p data-start="685" data-end="722"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Vercel</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1o1ahzk" data-start="724" data-end="750">✅ مثال (GitHub Pages):</h3>
<ol data-start="751" data-end="868">
<li data-section-id="1tbkv6d" data-start="751" data-end="765">
<p data-start="754" data-end="765">تنشئ حساب</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10zdnqv" data-start="766" data-end="792">
<p data-start="769" data-end="792">ترفع ملف <code data-start="778" data-end="790">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ey8jmz" data-start="793" data-end="815">
<p data-start="796" data-end="815">تفعل GitHub Pages</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1exm9gl" data-start="816" data-end="868">
<p data-start="819" data-end="868">يعطيك رابط مثل:<br data-start="834" data-end="837">
<code data-start="840" data-end="868">https://username.github.io</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="870" data-end="909">👉 والناس كلها تقدر تدخل عليه <strong data-start="900" data-end="909">مجاني</strong></p>
<hr data-start="911" data-end="914">
<h2 data-section-id="8n54ui" data-start="916" data-end="937">💰 متى تحتاج تدفع؟</h2>
<p data-start="938" data-end="951">تدفع فقط إذا:</p>
<ul data-start="952" data-end="1025">
<li data-section-id="13z0y3w" data-start="952" data-end="1002">
<p data-start="954" data-end="1002">تريد <strong data-start="959" data-end="975">اسم موقع خاص</strong> (domain مثل: mysite.com)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lyc22r" data-start="1003" data-end="1025">
<p data-start="1005" data-end="1025">أو تريد ميزات متقدمة</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1027" data-end="1075">لكن:<br>
✔ التعلم<br data-start="1040" data-end="1043">
✔ مواقع بسيطة<br data-start="1056" data-end="1059">
✔ مشاريع صغيرة</p>
<p data-start="1077" data-end="1113">→ كلها <strong data-start="1084" data-end="1113">تقدر تسويها بدون أي تكلفة</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1115" data-end="1118">
<h2 data-section-id="bsga9b" data-start="1120" data-end="1133">🔥 الخلاصة</h2>
<ul data-start="1134" data-end="1229">
<li data-section-id="2479yg" data-start="1134" data-end="1169">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1169">Notepad++ = فقط للكتابة (مجاني)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1dxu23o" data-start="1170" data-end="1192">
<p data-start="1172" data-end="1192">فتح الموقع = مجاني</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zhng50" data-start="1193" data-end="1229">
<p data-start="1195" data-end="1229">نشر الموقع = فيه طرق مجانية 100%</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1231" data-end="1234">
<p data-start="1236" data-end="1250">إذا تحب، أقدر:</p>
<ul data-start="1251" data-end="1355" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="pans7d" data-start="1251" data-end="1309">
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1309">أشرح لك <strong data-start="1261" data-end="1307">خطوة بخطوة كيف تنشر موقعك على GitHub Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3wqq8h" data-start="1310" data-end="1355" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1312" data-end="1355" data-is-last-node="">أو أعطيك <strong data-start="1321" data-end="1352">كود موقع كامل جاهز تبدأ فيه</strong> 🚀</p>
</li>
