وصلت لمرحلة مهمة جدًا—باقي خطوة واحدة فقط ويصير موقعك شغال!</p>
<hr data-start="106" data-end="109">
<h1 data-section-id="1ccbg5a" data-start="111" data-end="146">🚀 الآن ماذا تفعل؟ (تشغيل الموقع)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="ng6qzu" data-start="148" data-end="172">👇 اتبع الخطوات بدقة:</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="bfnti" data-start="174" data-end="203"><span role="text">1️⃣ اضغط على <strong data-start="191" data-end="203">Settings</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="204" data-end="236">في الأعلى (شوف الشريط اللي فيه):</p>
<ul data-start="237" data-end="283">
<li data-section-id="1uweazp" data-start="237" data-end="245">
<p data-start="239" data-end="245">Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sztk2" data-start="246" data-end="256">
<p data-start="248" data-end="256">Issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ir2fi" data-start="257" data-end="262">
<p data-start="259" data-end="262">…</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kjgj3" data-start="263" data-end="283">
<p data-start="265" data-end="283">👉 <strong data-start="268" data-end="280">Settings</strong> ⚙️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="285" data-end="288">
<h3 data-section-id="ocl6ia" data-start="290" data-end="316"><span role="text">2️⃣ ادخل إلى <strong data-start="307" data-end="316">Pages</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="317" data-end="338">بعد ما تضغط Settings:</p>
<ul data-start="340" data-end="393">
<li data-section-id="192yylo" data-start="340" data-end="368">
<p data-start="342" data-end="368">من القائمة الجانبية (يسار)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="89wa84" data-start="369" data-end="393">
<p data-start="371" data-end="393">اضغط على:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="384" data-end="393">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="395" data-end="398">
<h3 data-section-id="ortp28" data-start="400" data-end="424">3️⃣ فعل GitHub Pages</h3>
<p data-start="426" data-end="444">راح تشوف قسم اسمه:</p>
<p data-start="446" data-end="456"><strong data-start="446" data-end="456">Source</strong></p>
<p data-start="458" data-end="466">سوي كذا:</p>
<ul data-start="468" data-end="570">
<li data-section-id="1a60ftd" data-start="468" data-end="506">
<p data-start="470" data-end="506">اختار:<br data-start="476" data-end="479">
👉 <code data-start="484" data-end="506">Deploy from a branch</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ou3qyz" data-start="508" data-end="570">
<p data-start="510" data-end="516">تحتها:</p>
<ul data-start="519" data-end="570">
<li data-section-id="13p8zi0" data-start="519" data-end="541">
<p data-start="521" data-end="541">Branch: اختار <code data-start="535" data-end="541">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="220n1o" data-start="544" data-end="570">
<p data-start="546" data-end="570">Folder: خليها <code data-start="560" data-end="570">/ (root)</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="572" data-end="592">ثم:<br>
👉 اضغط <strong data-start="584" data-end="592">Save</strong></p>
<hr data-start="594" data-end="597">
<h3 data-section-id="19nzgln" data-start="599" data-end="631">⏳ 4️⃣ انتظر دقيقة أو دقيقتين</h3>
<hr data-start="633" data-end="636">
<h3 data-section-id="otyhcn" data-start="638" data-end="662">🔗 5️⃣ خذ رابط موقعك</h3>
<p data-start="664" data-end="691">بعدها راح يظهر لك رابط مثل:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="693" data-end="746"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 361px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://mik1mousa-prog.github.io/my-buisnisse</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="748" data-end="784">🎉 هذا موقعك الآن شغال على الإنترنت!</p>
<hr data-start="786" data-end="789">
<h1 data-section-id="702yxm" data-start="791" data-end="815">❗ إذا ما اشتغل مباشرة:</h1>
<ul data-start="816" data-end="862">
<li data-section-id="2bevmn" data-start="816" data-end="835">
<p data-start="818" data-end="835">انتظر دقيقة زيادة</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3karn8" data-start="836" data-end="862">
<p data-start="838" data-end="862">أو حدّث الصفحة (Refresh)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="864" data-end="867">
<h1 data-section-id="14x2087" data-start="869" data-end="887">💬 الخطوة الجاية</h1>
<p data-start="888" data-end="923">إذا اشتغل معك، قلّي:<br data-start="908" data-end="911">
👉 "اشتغل"</p>
<p data-start="925" data-end="939">وبعدها أساعدك:</p>
<ul data-start="940" data-end="995">
<li data-section-id="1q4uhr8" data-start="940" data-end="974">
<p data-start="942" data-end="974">نخلي الموقع شكله 🔥 (تصميم جميل)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nkk1ze" data-start="975" data-end="995">
<p data-start="977" data-end="995">أو نضيف صور وأزرار</p>
</li>
</ul>
