<hr data-start="107" data-end="110">
<h1 data-section-id="10ni08a" data-start="112" data-end="129">⏳ الآن وش تسوي؟</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="11bepa2" data-start="131" data-end="149">👉 1. انتظر شوي</h2>
<ul data-start="150" data-end="216">
<li data-section-id="1nlxxp" data-start="150" data-end="175">
