ass="ͼq">22</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">img</span><span> {</span><br><span>    width: </span><span class="ͼq">90</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>    max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">350</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">button</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">25</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">15</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    background: #38bdf8;</span><br><span>    border: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">12</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    cursor: </span><span class="ͼq">pointer</span><span>;</span><br><span>    transition: </span><span class="ͼq">0.3</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">button</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background: #0ea5e9;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">footer</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">14</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    opacity: </span><span class="ͼq">0.7</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"container"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span>مرحبا 👋</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>هذا موقعي الجديد 🔥</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">src</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"https://picsum.photos/400"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">alt</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"صورة"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;br&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;button</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">onclick</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span class="ͼt">playSound</span><span>()</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>🔊 اضغط للصوت</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;audio</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"sound"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;source</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">src</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"https://www.soundjay.com/buttons/sounds/button-3.mp3"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/audio&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;footer&gt;</span><br><span>    تم إنشاء الموقع بواسطة 💻</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/footer&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼn">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">playSound</span><span>() {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">document</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>getElementById(</span><span class="ͼr">"sound"</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>play();</span><br><span>}</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><br><span class