<hr data-start="115" data-end="118">
<h1 data-section-id="1g1phey" data-start="120" data-end="147">⚡ الطريقة الأسرع (الأفضل)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1tnwhdl" data-start="149" data-end="173">⌨️ باستخدام الكيبورد:</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1tffoj" data-start="175" data-end="196">🟢 على الكمبيوتر:</h3>
<ol data-start="197" data-end="226">
<li data-section-id="1wbkh2b" data-start="197" data-end="217">
<p data-start="200" data-end="217">اضغط داخل الكود</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ludflr" data-start="218" data-end="226">
<p data-start="221" data-end="226">اضغط:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="227" data-end="255"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 361px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Ctrl + A</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="256" data-end="272">👉 يحدد كل الكود</p>
<ol start="3" data-start="274" data-end="285">
<li data-section-id="1y48ddc" data-start="274" data-end="285">
<p data-start="277" data-end="285">ثم اضغط:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="286" data-end="312"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 361px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Delete</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="314" data-end="339">🎉 كذا انمسح كله مرة وحدة</p>
<hr data-start="341" data-end="344">
<h1 data-section-id="73vz4r" data-start="346" data-end="373">🖱️ طريقة ثانية (بالفأرة)</h1>
<ol data-start="375" data-end="436">
<li data-section-id="1rm5mkp" data-start="375" data-end="399">
<p data-start="378" data-end="399">اضغط في بداية الكود</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="k8wr6u" data-start="400" data-end="421">
<p data-start="403" data-end="421">اسحب إلى النهاية</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wllq9p" data-start="422" data-end="436">
<p data-start="425" data-end="436">اضغط Delete</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="438" data-end="452">(لكن أبطأ شوي)</p>
<hr data-start="454" data-end="457">
<h1 data-section-id="7uv6wm" data-start="459" data-end="478">📱 لو تستخدم جوال</h1>
<ul data-start="480" data-end="550">
<li data-section-id="evolwv" data-start="480" data-end="504">
<p data-start="482" data-end="504">اضغط مطول داخل الكود</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nvxmvv" data-start="505" data-end="541">
<p data-start="507" data-end="541">اختر <strong data-start="512" data-end="539">Select All (تحديد الكل)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10d4tp6" data-start="542" data-end="550">
<p data-start="544" data-end="550">ثم حذف</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="552" data-end="555">
<h1 data-section-id="6vn3op" data-start="557" data-end="572">💡 نصيحة مهمة</h1>
<p data-start="573" data-end="640">بعد ما تمسح:<br>
👉 مباشرة الصق الكود الجديد<br data-start="613" data-end="616">
👉 ثم احفظ أو <strong data-start="630" data-end="640">Commit</strong></p>
<hr data-start="642" data-end="645">
<h1 data-section-id="og2tuc" data-start="647" data-end="664">🚀 اختصار ذهبي:</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="665" data-end="710"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 361px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Ctrl + A → Delete → Paste</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="712" data-end="715">
<p data-start="717" data-end="745">💬 إذا تبغى، أقدر أعلمك بعد:</p>
<ul data-start="746" data-end="822" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="1th98gy" data-start="746" data-end="784">
<p data-start="748" data-end="784">كيف تعدل بسرعة بدون ما تمسح كل مرة</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tcrghr" data-start="785" data-end="822" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="787" data-end="822" data-is-last-node="">أو اختصارات تخليك تشتغل أسرع 10x 😎</p>
</li>
