<h2 data-section-id="wgngql" data-start="1865" data-end="1891">📤 2. ارفعهم على GitHub</h2>
<p data-start="1893" data-end="1934">في <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span>:</p>
